  <para id="eip-141">For difficult problems, most of these algorithms can require enormous computational resources â€” most experience a "combinatorial explosion": the amount of memory or computer time required becomes astronomical when the problem goes beyond a certain size. The search for more efficient problem solving algorithms is a high priority for AI research.[41]</para>


